name: MetaPlayers.gg
description: Whether you are a beginner or a professional gamer, MetaPlayers will give you the opportunity to perfect your gaming skills and improve yourself. Find and interact with other players, follow their streams or create your own gaming community. eSport is no longer just a hobby, it is one of the fastest growing online industry. Over 350 million people watched gaming related YouTube videos and Twitch streams just this year alone.
